            DevArmor is for engineering teams who want to move fast and keep
            their software compliant, without introducing friction.
          </p>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-5">
            <li>
              If you have a small team and recently started your AppSec program,
              DevArmor empowers your developers to make critical security
